<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>BugTracker</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script>
        // navegador + relogio
        document.onreadystatechange = () => {
            if(document.readyState === 'interactive') {
                document.getElementById("userAgent").value = window.navigator.userAgent
                document.getElementById("userDate").value = new Date()
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-light bg-light">
        <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">BugTracker</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
            Seu problema foi reportado com sucesso. Muito obrigado. <a href="/">Voltar e reportar mais um problema</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>